Name: team_size_condition
Description: Team size must be greater than 5

Name: sprint_duration_condition
Description: Sprint duration must be less than 30 days

Name: task_effort_condition
Description: Task effort must be less than 10 hours

Name: product_backlog_status_condition
Description: Product backlog status must be up-to-date

Name: release_plan_deviation_condition
Description: Release plan deviation must be less than 10%

Name: development_snapshot_quality_condition
Description: Development snapshot quality must be high

Name: feature_documentation_quality_condition
Description: Feature documentation quality must be high

Name: scrum_board_complexity_condition
Description: Scrum board complexity must be low

Name: sprint_review_feedback_condition
Description: Sprint review feedback must be positive

Name: sprint_goal_achievement_condition
Description: Sprint goal achievement must be high
